Abstract = {The influence of 10 different rootstocks was investigated for evaluating
   the most suitable rootstock for table grape cultivar Fantasy Seedless.
   The growth performance, photosynthesis, biochemical composition, and
   primary nutrients' status of the scion after grafting were investigated
   in `Fantasy Seedless' grafted on 10 different rootstocks. The studies on
   vegetative parameters revealed that the rootstock influences the
   vegetative growth thereby increasing the photosynthesis of a vine. The
   rootstock influenced the changes in biochemical constituents in the
