   Marlborough vineyard},
Booktitle = {XXIX INTERNATIONAL HORTICULTURAL CONGRESS ON HORTICULTURE: SUSTAINING
   LIVES, LIVELIHOODS AND LANDSCAPES (IHC2014): IV INTERNATIONAL SYMPOSIUM
