   development characteristics were determined, and carbohydrate
   accumulations and distributions at the graft area, under the graft area
   (rootstock), and above the graft area (scion) of the grafted grapevines
   in the dormant period were also determined. The highest graft success
   rate was 100.00\% in the combinations of `Rizessi'/SO4, `Rizellim'/SO4,
   `Rizpem'/SO4, `Rizellim'/110R, and `Rizpem'/110R. The percentage of vine
