   `Rizessi'/140Ru, `Rizessi'/SO4, `Rizessi'/110R, `celiksu'/SO4,
   `celiksu'/110R, `ulkemiz'/SO4, `Rizellim'/140Ru, `Rizellim'/SO4,
   `Rizpem'/SO4, and `Rizpem'/110R combinations showed a balanced
   distribution. The highest total carbohydrate accumulation (100.41 mg
   center dot L-1) was detected in the root region of the `ulkemiz'/SO4
