   Souza, Joyce Fagundes and da Silva Padilha, Carla Valeria and Pereira
   Basilio, Leticia Silva and Lima, Marcos dos Santos and Pereira, Giuliano
   Elias and Correa, Luiz Claudio and Vianello, Fabio and Pereira Lima,
   Giuseppina Pace and Moura, Mara Fernandes and Tecchio, Marco Antonio},
Title = {Phytochemical profile of Brazilian grapes (Vitis labrusca and hybrids)
